.TH "setup_ima_buffer" 9 "setup_ima_buffer" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
setup_ima_buffer \- add IMA buffer information to the fdt
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" setup_ima_buffer
.BI "(const struct kimage *image "  ","
.BI "void *fdt "  ","
.BI "int chosen_node "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "image" 12
kexec image being loaded.
.IP "fdt" 12
Flattened device tree for the next kernel.
.IP "chosen_node" 12
Offset to the chosen node.
.SH "RETURN"
0 on success, or negative errno on error.
